## Submission

Send to: `support@adyen.com`  
CC: `compliance@light.inc`

### Email Requirements

- Subject must include:
  - "Platform"
  - "Issuing Dispute Request"

- Body must include:
  - Number of disputes
  - Any reference IDs (e.g. transfer linkage)
  - Confirmation you are a platform

- Attach:
  - `disputes.zip`

---

## CSV Requirements

- Format: `.csv` only
- Recommended tools:
  - Excel
  - Google Sheets
- Delimiter: comma `,`

### Not Allowed

- `.xls` or other formats
- semicolon `;`
- tab delimiters

> Files not conforming to these requirements will be rejected.  
> Adyen Support will not reformat files.

